description:
For an international project in Chennai, we are urgently looking for a Full Remote Senior Power Platform Developer with \\+10 years of experience in functions such as design, development and implementation of application systems;.










 We are looking for a motivated contractor. Candidates need to be fluent in English.










**Tasks and responsibilities:** 



* Write Low Level Design, Unit Testing Plan, and Unit Test case documentation;
* Design, develop, code review, bug\\-fix, and test the application;
* Assist in Integration Testing and user acceptance testing;
* Perform Code optimization and strictly adhere to bank coding standards;
* Assist in any documentation or any artifacts needed for EA/OIS clearance;
* Coordinate day\\-to\\-day communication between team in other countries and HQ;
* Develop and maintain Dynamics 365/Power Platform/SharePoint Azure and .NET applications;
* Develop Dataverse plugins and debug existing applications for performance optimization;
* Build microservices (using lightweight APIs) that enable bidirectional integration through RESTful interfaces;
