* Knowledge of security processes and security controls;
* Excellent grasp and knowledge of industry best practices in the Dynamics 365 domain, with a successful track record of implementing projects in complex IT and business environments;
* Actively seeks and shares knowledge with others, effectively communicating and presenting information in a clear and organized manner;
* Organized, agile, persistent, and proactive, with the ability to juggle multiple tasks within tight deadlines;
* Delivers information effectively to support the team or workgroup, with strong writing and editing skills in English, conveying complex ideas clearly and directly;
* Hands\\-on experience in developing Power Automate to support Backend jobs, bulk updates to dataverse, connection to SharePoint, 0365\\. Etc;
* Experience working with Azure DevOps and continuous integration;
* Fluent in English;
